        title: "DateInterval, DatePeriod și calcule complexe",
        content: "DATEINTERVAL — reprezentare interval de timp:\n```php\n<?php\n// Constructie interval:\n$interval = new DateInterval('P1Y2M10DT2H30M');\n// P = Period\n// 1Y = 1 an, 2M = 2 luni, 10D = 10 zile\n// T = separator timp\n// 2H = 2 ore, 30M = 30 minute\n\n$start = new DateTimeImmutable('2025-01-01');\n$end = $start->add($interval);\necho $end->format('d.m.Y'); // 11.03.2026\n\n// Diferenta intre doua date:\n$nastere = new DateTimeImmutable('1998-05-20');\n$azi = new DateTimeImmutable();\n$varsta = $nastere->diff($azi);\necho \"Vârsta: \" . $varsta->y . \" ani, \" . $varsta->m . \" luni\";\n```\n\nDATEPERIOD — iterarea intervalelor:\n```php\n<?php\n// Toate zilele dintr-o lună:\n$start = new DateTimeImmutable('2025-01-01');\n$end   = new DateTimeImmutable('2025-02-01');\n$interval = new DateInterval('P1D'); // 1 zi\n\n$period = new DatePeriod($start, $interval, $end);\nforeach ($period as $zi) {\n    echo $zi->format('d.m.Y') . \" (\" . $zi->format('l') . \")\\n\";\n}\n// 01.01.2025 (Wednesday)\n// 02.01.2025 (Thursday)\n// ... etc pana la 31.01.2025\n\n// Toate luni pe un an:\n$start = new DateTimeImmutable('2025-01-01');\n$end   = new DateTimeImmutable('2026-01-01');\n$lunar = new DatePeriod($start, new DateInterval('P1M'), $end);\nforeach ($lunar as $luna) {\n    echo $luna->format('F Y') . \"\\n\"; // January 2025, February 2025...\n}\n```\n\nCALCUL ZILE LUCRĂTOARE:\n```php\n<?php\nfunction zileeLucrătoare(DateTimeImmutable $start, DateTimeImmutable $end): int {\n    $count = 0;\n    $period = new DatePeriod($start, new DateInterval('P1D'), $end);\n    foreach ($period as $zi) {\n        $dayOfWeek = (int)$zi->format('N'); // 1=Lun, 7=Dum\n        if ($dayOfWeek <= 5) $count++; // Luni-Vineri\n    }\n    return $count;\n}\n```",
