        order: 4,
        title: "Laravel Sanctum — API Authentication",
        content: "Laravel Sanctum = autentificare ușoară pentru SPA + API tokens. Parte din Laravel.\n\n```bash\ncomposer require laravel/sanctum\nphp artisan vendor:publish --provider=\"Laravel\\Sanctum\\SanctumServiceProvider\"\nphp artisan migrate\n```\n\nAPI TOKEN AUTH (pentru aplicații mobile/externe):\n```php\n<?php\n// Login — generare token:\nclass AuthController extends Controller {\n    public function login(Request $request): JsonResponse {\n        $validated = $request->validate([\n            'email'    => 'required|email',\n            'password' => 'required',\n        ]);\n        \n        if (!Auth::attempt($validated)) {\n            return response()->json(['error' => 'Credențiale invalide'], 401);\n        }\n        \n        $user = Auth::user();\n        $token = $user->createToken(\n            'api-token',\n            ['read', 'write'] // abilities/scopes\n        )->plainTextToken;\n        \n        return response()->json([\n            'user'  => new UserResource($user),\n            'token' => $token,\n        ]);\n    }\n    \n    public function logout(Request $request): JsonResponse {\n        $request->user()->currentAccessToken()->delete();\n        return response()->json(['message' => 'Deconectat']);\n    }\n}\n\n// Protejare route-uri cu Sanctum:\nRoute::middleware('auth:sanctum')->group(function () {\n    Route::get('/user', fn(Request $r) => new UserResource($r->user()));\n    Route::apiResource('produse', ProdusController::class);\n});\n\n// Client (React/mobile) trimite:\n// Authorization: Bearer 1|abc123def456...\n```\n\nSPA AUTH (cookies, mai sigur față de localStorage):\n```php\n<?php\n// config/cors.php + config/sanctum.php — set domain\n// Blade/SPA aceeași origine sau CORS configurat\n\n// CSRF cookie pentru SPA:\n// GET /sanctum/csrf-cookie   → setează cookie\n// Apoi POST /login\n```",
